comments: Noel (OKC) and Whiteside (POR) engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Whiteside (POR) firms up in a screening position in Schroder's (OKC) path.
Tolliver (POR) makes contact with Paul (OKC) as he retrieves the pass and affects his SQBR.
Gallinari (OKC) makes marginal contact to Hood's (POR) body during his drive, while Noel (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs contact.
At the end of Hood's (POR) drive, the ball goes off of Noel's (OKC) leg and Hood legally recovers the ball and passes.
Lillard (POR) draws Schroder (OKC) into the air, but Schroder jumps to the side of Lillard and lands in a legal guarding position before Lillard initiates contact on the jump shot attempt.
Lillard's (POR) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim prior to the expiration of the shot clock.
Tolliver (POR) sets the screen in Schroder's (OKC) path and does not deliver contact.
Diallo (OKC) turns his body and delivers contact to Tolliver (POR) as he sets the screen.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) attempts a take foul on Lillard (POR) but the contact is marginal.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Tolliver (POR) briefly engages with Gallinari (OKC) during the inbound before disengaging.
Gallinari (OKC) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Bazemore (POR) makes contact with Paul (OKC) during the drive, but Paul is able to move through the marginal contact.
Bazemore (POR) makes marginal contact to Paul (OKC) on the driving shot attempt.
